---
title: Seared Snapper & Creamy Dill Sauce with Parsnip Mash & Zesty Greens
description: We’ve gone a little bit fancy on you with this snazzy snapper, coated in a creamy dill sauce and loaded with delicate and aromatic flavours. Accompanied by crunchy broccolini and a smooth mash, you won't believe you whipped up such a delight.
